snippet.title: The Wardrobe - Even Better Edition - PC ReLaunch Trailer
snippet.description: The award-winning PC graphic adventure paying homage to the great classics of the '90s is now available in a shiny edition, with new features and extra contents not included in the original version (but free for who already owns it!)
